snippet.title: USHempTV
snippet.description: USHempTV is the official YouTube channel for the U.S. Hemp Roundtable @hemproudtable, the nation's leading advocate for the full legalization of all hemp-derived ingredients and products. The  U.S. Hemp Roundtable a coalition made up of America's leading hemp and CBD companies, organizations, and advocates committed to ensuring safe hemp and CBD products. Learn more and take action at hempsupporter.com.
